<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞过天空，手里抓着沉重的车辆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”地上的一个人大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿的手拿着一辆公交车！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有一辆出租车！”另一个人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西找到了一个安全而寂静的街道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把车放了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你，火箭女孩儿！”公交车上的一个女人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是我的英雄，火箭女孩儿！”出租车司机说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48281</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很乐意为大家服务！”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48282</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53205</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西重新飞向天空，又回到了西街。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那里依然大雪纷飞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>风刮得很大，雪积得越来越厚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘我从来没见过这么大的暴风雪！’罗西心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69607</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看到两辆警车几乎都要被埋在雪里了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69608</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>警察们正试图把车挖出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“气象员朝哪个方向走了？”罗西问那些警察。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他往那边去了，朝那个山的方向。”一个警察喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跟随着货车的轮胎印追了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寒风呼啸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪花飘来飘去，几乎把货车的车轮轨迹都覆盖住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西使用了她的超级视觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>隔着密集的雪花，她看到远处有一束微弱的灯光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他在那儿！”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115072</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在是时候阻止这个坏蛋了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115073</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西很快就追赶上了货车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她深深地吸了一口气。然后……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>呼——！罗西使尽全力吐出一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131540</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她吹起了一阵强风。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131541</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135774</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>气象员的货车前形成了一个巨大的雪堆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哐！货车撞进了雪堆里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要报仇，火箭女孩儿！”气象员大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从货车里跳出来，手里拿着一个气象球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在他要扔球的时候——嗞轰！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西用眼里发射出的激光把球炸成了碎片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你今天再也不能制造坏天气了！”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你会坐牢的，气象员！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”气象员说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177081</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太有意思了！”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177082</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不敢相信真的下雪了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克，玛拉和特勒尔正在特勒尔家的后院堆雪人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想知道罗西什么时候回来。”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她已经离开很久了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195074</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊。”玛拉说，“她错过了所有有趣的事情！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我回来了！”罗西叫着跑到院子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“竟然下雪了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔用怀疑的眼神看着罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道火箭女孩儿是不是跟这件事情有关系。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227876</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁知道呢？”罗西笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>